'''Santa Marcela''' is a 5th class [[Philippine municipality|municipality]] in the [[Philippine province|province]] of [[Apayao province|Apayao]], [[Philippines]]. According to the [[2000]] census, it has a population of 9,856 people in 1,995 households.

Santa Marcela and [[Pudtol, Apayao|Pudtol]], Apayao were originally territories of [[Luna, Apayao|Luna]] before they gained their own municipal status.

==Deng Barangay==

Ing Santa Marcela atin yang 13 [[barangay]].

* Barocboc
* Consuelo
* Imelda (Sipa Annex)
* Malekkeg
* Marcela (Pob.)
* Nueva
* Panay
* San Antonio
* Sipa Proper
* Emiliana
* San Carlos
* San Juan
* San Mariano

